@c ----------------------------------------------------------------------
@node remquo, math
@findex remquo
@subheading Syntax

@example
#include <math.h>

double remquo(double x, double y, int *quo);
@end example

@subheading Description

@code{remquo} returns the same remainder as @code{remainder}, and also places
at least the three lower bits of the quotient in *@var{quo}.

@subheading Return Value

The remainder of @math{@var{x}/@var{y}}.

@subheading Portability

@portability ansi, posix
